title: AHS: Asylum - Thredson mistreats Lana
author: AHS VIDEOS
comment: Ik he's a serial killer but he looks so adorable when he laughs and puts his hand over his mouth at the beginning
This is why you never trust men with bushy eyebrows !!!😂😂

I thought he was the nicest person
Well I was wrong

I like that they've obviously done their homework here, Harlow's work is something I had to learn in psychology (a classmate and I are using that to make our teacher watch this. She already sorta knows him from Heroes anyway, so it's not an unknown quantity). I like that he's comparing himself to the baby monkeys though, because they grew up to be incredibly antisocial, got bullied a lot, had little luck with the opposite sex (well, boys didn't, I don't think girls had that choice) and made very poor parents, frequently killing their own offspring. He seems to tick three of those boxes and I wonder if he'd've ticked the last
